snippet.title: Noxious Weeds - Gameplay Trailer #roguelite #bulletheaven
snippet.description:
Noxious Weeds - Coming in Early Access on January 9, 2024
Wishlist now on Steam ▶️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2429310/Noxious_Weeds?utm_source=yt_seg&utm_campaign=EA_trailer
Unlock all the Steam achievements in the FREE Demo!

Face the corruption that poisons your harvest! Noxious Weeds is an action rogue-lite where you slay hordes of creatures with the help of cute veggies and a combination of your favorite tools. The harvest is power. Choose wisely!

Join the community: https://discord.gg/pAjdJJSJxa
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SolarEclipse_G
Press Kit: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1KTwJaUnJsUvrrm8WzkzfeBAPR7gcJWig?usp=sharing
